        "pf_1afb353b_value": "We get it. You’ve already spent hundreds, maybe even thousands of euros on treatments that promised results but ended up disappointing you.<br><br>That’s why you get a full 30 days to try. No vague conditions. No annoying questions. If it doesn’t work for you, just let us know and you get your money back, simple as that.",
